{"tid":1892604,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】一駐守警察總部女警出現病徵等待測試結果　","createTime":"2020-02-22T15:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T15:44:36.000Z","uid":282979,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bd28365ad13341c0d27f6e1173d9e8c8f1b88d7b","tid":1892604,"uid":282979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"本港早前錄得首宗警員感染武漢新型冠狀病毒，病人是一名 48 歲男防暴警察，曾在 2 月 18 日與 59 人出席一個退休警員派對。警方回覆《立場新聞》指，截至今日晚上 7 時，再有1名警員出現病徵，累計有病徵的警員增至 5 人。據警方消息指，最新出現病徵的警員是一名女警，駐守警察總部，現正在瑪嘉烈醫院留院等候快速測試結果。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，其中 2 人經接受醫院治療後已出院並入住檢疫中心，初步檢疫結果呈陰性；另外 3 人出現病徵的警務人員仍在醫院接受治療，當中 2 人的初步檢疫結果呈陰性，1人正等候檢測結果。<br />\n<br />\n警方指高度關注事件，會積極配合衞生署進行病理學追蹤，包括提交該名警員過去 14 日的工作記錄和執勤表等資料。<br />\n<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32indDf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32indDf&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=0afbddeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32indDf</a>"},{"pid":"b126ce374ad5e9797abcd0264cbbcb78eee46b12","tid":1892604,"uid":282979,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDSSJq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDSSJq6.jpg&h=5aed773f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ba6ee0abcdbe2a8a9fbbbaf5557cd73b4342727","tid":1892604,"uid":61615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"上呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a772b6ed9a0235bcd22998097af8b31935db9d4","tid":1892604,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68da52c6da27094752e9d977aa12f1047cff332f","tid":1892604,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T1